databaseQueries.query: SELECT count(*) as aggregate FROM "reports" inner join "respondents" on "respondents"."id" = "reports"."respondent_id" inner join "questions" on "questions"."id" = "reports"."question_id" WHERE "respondents"."unit_id" = 1 and "reports"."created_at"::text like '%2022-09%' and "reports"."deleted_at" IS NULL
